{"tid":919744,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好懷緬九十年代香港嘅娛樂圈","createTime":"2018-11-28T09:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T06:44:59.000Z","uid":206673,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a602f965129e4418dc90c9d382fd97134239748","tid":919744,"uid":206673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:30:37.000Z","msg":"當時真係亞洲一哥<br />\n歌壇有四大天王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 王傑李克勤伊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 王菲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個歌手都紅到全亞洲都識<br />\n影壇都有四大天王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有極多高質港產電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他國家都爭住買我地電影<br />\n<br />\n當年嘅光景真係一去不復返"},{"pid":"ae21152078d82d38f2b66790eed4451d97d57a1f","tid":919744,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:16:41.000Z","msg":"成龍先係紅遍全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n九十年代亦都係香港最光輝既時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d4cfb84953e6ec2bfca9ebf86abac3bb60c5f3","tid":919744,"uid":204222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"影壇都有四大天王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6734e3979e8f274af2709534c948f601e7e91d21","tid":919744,"uid":8021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"以前啲明星真係高質好多"},{"pid":"03d41a37c04e878fb221031e62287ae5558ce9dc","tid":919744,"uid":206673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0d4cfb84953e6ec2bfca9ebf86abac3bb60c5f3","tid":919744,"uid":204222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"影壇都有四大天王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif